aysaa aaladaha la oggolaaday sida taleefankaaga inay oggaadaan oo ay ka maamulaan Codex kombiyuutarkan`,\"codexMobile.setupDialog.allowHost.error\":`Xakamaynta fog lama suurtagelin in la hawlgeliyo. Mar kale isku day`,\"codexMobile.setupDialog.allowHost.heading\":`Miyaad u oggolaaneysaa in aaladaha ay xakameeyaan kombiyuutarkan?`,\"codexMobile.setupDialog.allowHost.primary\":`Oggolow`,\"codexMobile.setupDialog.allowHost.title\":`Miyaad u oggolaanaysaa in aaladaha ay xakameeyaan kombiyuutarkan?`,"},{"line":5,"text":"- Haddii aadan hubin, dooro inaad ku darto TODO oo leh qoraal gaaban halkii aad wax ka alifi lahayd.`,\"home.useCases.agentsDocsSync.prompt\":`Cusboonaysii AGENTS.md adigoo ku daraya habraacyo iyo amarro cusub.`,\"home.useCases.changelogUpdate.automationPrompt\":`Cusboonaysii diiwaanka isbeddellada adigoo ku daraya qodobada ugu muhiimsan ee toddobaadkan iyo xiriiriyeyaasha PR-yada muhiimka ah. Xaddidaadaha: - Kaliya ku dar qodobbo ay taageerayso taariikhda repo-ga. - Qaab-dhismeedka ka dhig mid fudud oo waafaqsan qaabka diiwaanka isbeddellada ee jira.`,\"home.useCases.changelogUpdate.prompt\":`Ku cusboonaysii diiwaanka isbeddelka waxyaabaha ugu muhiimsan ee toddobaadkan.`,\"home.useCases.ciMonitor.automationPrompt\":`Hubi fashilaadaha CI; u kala saar sababta ugu badan ee loo malaynayo inay ka dambeeyaan, kuna soo jeedi xalalka ugu yar ee lagu sixi karo. Xeerarka caddaynta: - Soo xigo shaqooyinka, tijaabooyinka, khaladaadka, iyo caddeynta log-yada. - Si aad log-yada u gasho, isticmaal isdhexgal"},{"line":8,"text":"unknown {Lama garanayo in pull request-kan la mideyn karo} other {Pull request-kan weli diyaar uma aha in la mideeyo}}`,\"pullRequestsPage.detail.actions.merge.menuItem\":`Isku-biiri`,\"pullRequestsPage.detail.actions.merge.trigger\":`Isku-biiri`,\"pullRequestsPage.detail.actions.refreshing\":`Dib u soo kicinaya falalka`,\"pullRequestsPage.detail.actions.repoRestrictionError\":`Amarada la isku daray waxaa laga xidhay gudaha kaydkan`,\"pullRequestsPage.detail.actions.repoRestrictionError.description\":`Isku day mar labbaad si loo isticmaalo isku darka. Haddii ay taas guulaysato, Codex waxay kaydin doonaan nooca sidii qaabka isku darkaaga PR ee asalka ah`,\"pullRequestsPage.detail.activity\":`Hawl`,\"pullRequestsPage.detail.activity.errorTitle\":`Soo saari kari waayay hawsha isbeddelka la soo jeediyay`,\"pullRequestsPage.detail.activity.loadingAuthor\":`Soo saaraya hawsha`,\"pullRequestsPage.detail.activityApproved\":`Waxaa ansixiyay`,\"pullRequestsPage.detail.activityChangesRequested\":`Isbeddello uu codsa"}]},{"path":"Z:\\01_PROJECTS\\apps\\Tiiextension\\dashboard\\assets\\solidity-CcAHyI74.js","matches":[{"line":1,"text":"var e=[Object.freeze(JSON.parse(`{\"displayName\":\"Solidity\",\"fileTypes\":[\"sol\"],\"name\":\"solidity\",\"patterns\":[{\"include\":\"#natspec\"},{\"include\":\"#declaration-userType\"},{\"include\":\"#comment\"},{\"include\":\"#operator\"},{\"include\":\"#global\"},{\"include\":\"#control\"},{\"include\":\"#constant\"},{\"include\":\"#primitive\"},{\"include\":\"#type-primitive\"},{\"include\":\"#type-modifier-extended-scope\"},{\"include\":\"#declaration\"},{\"include\":\"#function-call\"},{\"include\":\"#assembly\"},{\"include\":\"#punctuation\"}],\"repository\":{\"assembly\":{\"patterns\":[{\"match\":\"\\\\\\\\b(assembly)\\\\\\\\b\",\"name\":\"keyword.control.assembly\"},{\"match\":\"\\\\\\\\b(let)\\\\\\\\b\",\"name\":\"storage.type.assembly\"}]},\"comment\":{\"patterns\":[{\"include\":\"#comment-line\"},{\"include\":\"#comment-block\"}]},\"comment-block\":{\"begin\":\"/\\\\\\\\*\",\"end\":\"\\\\\\\\*/\",\"name\":\"comment.block\",\"patterns\":[{\"include\":\"#comment-todo\"}]},\"comment-line\":{\"begin\":\"(?<!tp:)//\",\"end\":\"$\",\"name\":\"comment.line\",\"patterns\":[{\"include\":\"#comment-todo\"}]},\"comment-todo\":{\"match\":\"(?i)\\\\\\\\b(F"}]},{"path":"Z:\\01_PROJECTS\\apps\\Tiiextension\\dashboard\\assets\\sortable.esm-C8WT2h5L.js","matches":[{"line":1,"text":"import{